com.fxgraph.graph

Class CartesianGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fxgraph.graph.Graph
      • com.fxgraph.graph.CartesianGraph

  • public class CartesianGraph
extends Graph
    A specialized graph that plots data in the Cartesian x,y plane.

    A single cartesian graph can plot many datasets on the same set of axes.

    Since:
    17 August 2021
    Author:
    ogallagher (javadoc)

        Add a new point to the graph.
        Parameters:
        point - The point to add.
        plotName - The plot to add this point to. If null, the default plot will be used, or a new plot with a generated name if there are no plots available.
